node.text:
Driven by innovation. Inspiring performance. Intelligent versatility. The all-new ID.4 – the next-generation SUV. For a life off the beaten track. 100% SUV. 100% electric. And 100% Volkswagen.
 
#VWID4 #electricSUV #eSUV #justelectric

Electricity consumption, kWh/100 km: combined 16,9 – 16,2; CO2 emission combined, g/ km; Efficiency class: A+. Video shows optional equipment. Displayed version may vary from actual product.
